·弗里尔（Sarah Friar）已经向其他公司高层领导表示，她担心如果公司收入增长不够迅速，可能无法支付未来的数据中心合同费用。 对此，OpenAI 表示，企业和广告业务正在增长。OpenAI 爆出大利空！两项关键指标均未「达标」，CFO：增速不够，将没钱买算力！AI 股集体跳水，英伟达、英特尔、甲骨文齐跌｜美股开盘 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-056fa965746f12ec5c2c5431e80181b3_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "135 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2032593268840600541"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIls/ClfOh3u19EAMaCTExOTMxODc2MyDfk8PPBjAAOKsBQA5yEzIwMzI1OTMyNjg4NDA2MDA1NDF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1777480085.263197", "card_id": "Q_271047255", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 67}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么狗狗见面先闻屁股，这是什么坏习惯？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "为什么狗狗见面先闻屁股，这是什么坏习惯？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-86f3c1dc27e71648f82b0abc50d18730_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "129 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/271047255"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ils/ClfOh3u19EAMaCDIyNTA3NzY5IJXdkdYFMAA4tQFAD3IJMjcxMDQ3MjU1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1777480085.263565", "card_id": "Q_40151168", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "既然果糖这么不好，我们到底该不该吃水果？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "看到各种资料说到果糖不能像葡萄糖那样被人体转化，水果中就含有大量果糖，我们究竟该不该吃水果？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-1de729f29860ab80b848dc3d8b141dc0_qhd.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "119 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/40151168"}}, "attached_info":